<p><span>Today, Joe and Brian discuss WordPress in the â€œenterprise,&#8221; starting with a discussion on what the enterprise even is. We discuss WordPressâ€™s value to the enterprise, and what enterprise level companies are looking for in their technology solutions.</span></p>
<p><span>The conversation turns into conspiracy theories and joking around by the 50 minute mark, so donâ€™t be intimidated by the hour and fifteen minute timestamp.</span></p>
