<p>Joe and Brian were joined by Ryan McCue, the Lead Developer of the REST API, Daniel Bachhuber, a contributing developer to the REST API, and K.Adam White, Aaron Jorbin, and Jack Lenox â€” each with unique experiences using the REST API. They discussed the talks from A Day of REST, but also about the impact of the new API more broadly as well.</p>
<p>If youâ€™re at all interested in the REST API, this is an excellent round table to listen to.</p>
